inquiries.query:
/*
In the job postings fact table get the job id, job_title_short, job location, job_via, and salary year_avg columns.
Only return rows where the job location is in 'Tampa, FL'

*/

SELECT
	job_id,
    job_title_short,
    job_location,
    job_via,
    salary_year_avg
FROM 
	job_postings_fact
WHERE 
	job_location == 'Tampa, FL'
inquiries.name: com practice problem-1
